{"tid":252076,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【自古以來日本。。。】2千年前中國青銅幣在日本出土","createTime":"2017-05-21T12:36:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-22T11:23:16.000Z","uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3d081a6da61c4add6d49da32848d0913140049c7","tid":252076,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T12:36:38.000Z","msg":"【考古大發現】2千年前中國青銅幣在日本出土？ 唔係時空交錯！<br />\n<br />\n最後更新: 0520 15:07&nbsp;/&nbsp;建立時間 (HKT): 0520 09:07<br />\n<br />\n日本傳媒報道，日本兵庫縣南淡路島市教育委員會宣佈，在該市的「入田稻荷前」遺跡中出土了3枚被稱為「貨泉」的青銅幣。<span style=\"color: red;\">這種貨幣於公元14到40年間（王莾篡漢至東漢光武中興）在中國鑄造，並於彌生時代（約公元前300年至公元後250年；即戰國時代至東漢）傳至日本</span>。<br />\n<br />\n報道稱，南淡路島市教委表示，包括本次在內，日本國內共發現179枚「貨泉」，但像本次這樣數枚錢幣呈重疊狀態被發現的情況極為罕見。<br />\n<br />\n南淡路島市教委負責人表示，「傳來古代中國貨幣，成為證明在彌生時代後期淡路島是海上貿易要衝的重要史料」。<br />\n<br />\n日本經濟新聞網/ 參考消息網<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170520/56718034\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170520%2F56718034&d=t4UGmyAz6k58H4TqneELPlKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=09763e80\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170520%2F56718034&h=4d39807c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170520/56718034</a>"},{"pid":"735a46d9c21e4a256780a87c9cb4ea7c51bc85d7","tid":252076,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T12:37:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06a1c506268cf859c8810dcf43705dcf9ff6b58a","tid":252076,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T12:38:42.000Z","msg":"日本有用漢字"},{"pid":"3dc7fc3da2ac7a38d463293b1e74996ba458ab66","tid":252076,"uid":24133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T13:02:37.000Z","msg":"又有機會俾支那打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c4b472913fc27eb3f003b8a7447c1bdd1cbcd3f